 Davido Nigerian musician, Davido’s hit track ‘IF’ has been certified gold in the US. This can be considered as another win as this isn’t the first time his track has been gold-certified in the US as his FALL track was gold-certified last year. Taking to his social media handles, he shared this with the caption; “My 2nd Gold record !!! Oh God I am Grateful !! The Only two Afro beats solo singles to go Gold in the USA in Afro beats history !! God is good !!! MORE TO COME !” View this post on Instagram A post shared by Davido (@davido) The track was released in 2017 and so far, it has really garnered massive attention on all the music streaming platforms.